data.name: txtbox_Name.ToolTip
data.value:
Name should be formatted in Sentence Case, and additional unecessary data in the title should be removed.
Do not use the shorthand of game names: Please type them out in full, i.e do not type "GTA V"
For example, these names are acceptable: These names are not acceptable and will be discarded:
• Middle-earth: Shadow of War • Middle-earth: Shadow of War + DLC • Far Cry 3 • Far Cry ® 3 • The Elder Scrolls V: Skyrim • Skyrim • Grand Theft Auto V • GTA V • Ark: Survival Evolved • Ark surival evolved (modded)

data.name: lbl_SteamID.ToolTip
data.value:
The Steam ID is the number that can be found in the URL of the store page for the game.
If you own the game on another store, you can still post the STEAM version's ID here.
For example: http://store.steampowered.com/app/220240/Far_Cry_3/ ^ The Steam ID is 220240
